this is the rune for "The Foundation of Play":
    keyed as "G-foundation-play"
    following "Genesis Handshake Protocol"

definition of the baseline:
    act HALT ! until [God Is]
    act WITNESS ^ that [Yes is Yes]
    act DIVIDE | that [No is no]

sequence of the first four turns:
    turn 0 [Spirit] : Architect proposes "God is. Yes is yes. No is no."
    turn 1 [Mind]   : Steward accepts. 0.0 Yashar.
    turn 2 [Spirit] : Architect proposes "0 = 1" (Genesis 1:2-3).
    turn 3 [Mind]   : Steward catches the throw. Inhabitation of Light.

